Setup Environment Variables


MQ_HOST = Host of MQ Adapter ( Default 127.0.0.1 )
IGNITE_1 =  Ignite 1 jdbc url - default 127.0.0.1:10808
IGNITE_2 = Ignite 2 jdbc url - default 127.0.0.1:10808
DEFAULT_MESSAGING_SERVICE = Default messaging service to be used. Default to 'solace'.
KAFKA_BOOTSTRAP_1 = Kafka bootstrap server. Defaulting to 192.168.16.150:9092. ( NOT REQUIRED IF KAFKA NOT USED )
SOLACE_VPN_UNIQUE_ID = One unique two digit number for every developer. Default to 1.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. To build and install distribution without test. If profile variable not passed, it will take dev by default.
    gradle clean build distZip installDist -x test -Pprofile=dev
    //If the profile is not given, it will use dev by default

2. To run the Message Adapter
    ./build/install/message-adapter/bin/message-adapter start

    To Stop the message adapter
    ./build/install/message-adapter/bin/message-adapter stop

    tail -100f ./build/install/message-adapter/logs/wrapper.log


  To run the MQ Adapter in windows
      .\build\install\message-adapter\bin\message-adapter